npx tsc --noEmit
npm run build

Then npm run dev and test this flow:
•	1. / redirects to /auth/login
•	2. Sign up → confirm email → sign in → lands on /
•	3. Home shows skeletons then empty state (no projects yet)
•	4. Create project at /projects/new — avatar preview reacts to color
