•	6. Home replans and shows tasks
•	7. Tap Start Work → /session/focus, stopwatch runs
•	8. Click task checkmark → turns green
•	9. Stop → session saved, home reloads with new plan
•	10. /logs shows session with correct local time
•	11. /projects/[id] shows tasks grouped by milestone, task 2 locked
•	12. Long-press task 1 → mark done → task 2 unlocks automatically
•	13. Open project select → toggle active/paused, Done re-plans
