Common fixes:
•	'cookies() must be in request scope' — server.ts only used in Server Components and Route Handlers
•	RLS permission denied — re-run all 5 RLS policies in Supabase SQL Editor
•	Planner returns empty — add console.log(plan) to check tasks have status=pending and projects status=active
•	DiceBear not loading — check network, try with a public URL in browser directly

